=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Overviews_Operators_ex49 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 1002 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, energy distribution is late, and filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: sustained
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: late

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1002.1316
  harmonic_decay_rate: -3.2695
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0837
  pitch_clarity: 203.8063
  inharmonicity: 0.0006
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -1.1963
  resonance_freq: 1033.5938

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
